#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "Autostart Manager"
msgstr "Menedżer autostartu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:30
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This module is a configuration tool for managing what programs start up "
#| "with &kde;. It allows you to add programs or scripts so they "
#| "automatically start during the startup of &kde; and to manage them."
msgid ""
"This module is a configuration tool for managing what programs start up with "
"your personal &plasma;. It allows you to add programs or scripts so they "
"automatically run during startup or shutdown of your &plasma; session and to "
"manage them."
msgstr ""
"Narzędzie konfiguracyjne dla programów uruchamianych podczas startu &kde;. "
"Pozwala dodawać i zarządzać programami i skryptami, które będą uruchamiane "
"automatycznie wraz ze startem &kde;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Please note that in this module all changes are immediately applied."
msgstr "Wszystkie zmiany w tym module są natychmiast akceptowane."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The program scans <filename>~/.config/autostart/</filename>, your "
#| "<filename class=\"directory\">KDE Autostart</filename> folder (<filename "
#| "class=\"directory\">$KDEHOME/Autostart</filename> as default), <filename "
#| "class=\"directory\">$KDEHOME/env</filename> and <filename class="
#| "\"directory\">$KDEHOME/shutdown</filename> folders to check what programs "
#| "and scripts are already there and displays them. It allows you to manage "
#| "them easily."
msgid ""
"The program scans <filename>$HOME/.config/autostart/</filename> for "
"applications and login scripts, <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.config/"
"plasma-workspace/env</filename> for pre-startup scripts and <filename class="
"\"directory\">$HOME/.config/plasma-workspace/shutdown</filename> for logout "
"scripts to check what programs and scripts are already there and displays "
"them. It allows you to manage them easily."
msgstr ""
"Program przeszukuje katalogi <filename>~/.config/autostart/</filename>, Twój "
"katalog <filename class=\"directory\">KDE Autostart</filename> (domyślnie "
"<filename class=\"directory\">$KDEHOME/Autostart</filename>), <filename "
"class=\"directory\">$KDEHOME/env</filename> i <filename class=\"directory\">"
"$KDEHOME/shutdown</filename>, aby sprawdzić, które programy i skrypty już "
"się w nich znajdują. Ułatwia to zarządzanie nimi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Login scripts are <filename class=\"extension\">.desktop</filename> files "
"with a <literal>X-KDE-AutostartScript=true</literal> key. Pre-startup "
"scripts are run earlier and can be used to set environment variables."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:40
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Note that you can change the location of the <filename class=\"directory"
#| "\">Autostart</filename> folder in the <guilabel>About Me</guilabel> tab "
#| "in &systemsettings; and set a different folder than <filename class="
#| "\"directory\">$KDEHOME/Autostart</filename>."
msgid ""
"Note that you can change the location of your <filename class=\"directory"
"\">Autostart</filename> folder in <menuchoice><guimenu>Applications</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Locations</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the "
"<guilabel>Personalization</guilabel> category of the &systemsettings; and "
"set a different folder than <filename class=\"directory\">$HOME/.config/"
"autostart</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Możesz zmienić położenie katalogu <filename class=\"directory\">Autostart</"
"filename> w karcie <guilabel>O mnie</guilabel> w &systemsettings-"
"miejscownik; i ustawić katalog inny niż <filename class=\"directory\">"
"$KDEHOME/Autostart</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please read also <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/kcmsmserver\">Desktop Session</"
"ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/kded\">Background Services</ulink> "
"for information how to configure the startup behavior of your &plasma; "
"session."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some &kde; applications handle the autostart behavior on their own, &eg; you "
"can enable or disable autostart of an application in the settings dialog "
"(&kalarm;) or you have to use <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (&konversation;, "
"&kopete;), otherwise the application is still running in the systemtray and "
"will be restarted on next login."
msgstr ""

